  "description": "\"Hey, Boss! We got trouble! The Red Dragon Knights were spotted in a village nearby!\"\n\"Calm down. We just need to make ourselves scarce before—\"\n\"Too late! Throw down your weapons, bandit scum!\"\n\"What?! The Crimson Valkyrie?!\"\n\"But how?! That village is hours from here!\"\n\"Unfortunately for you, we run this far before breakfast every morning. In armor. Isn't that right?\"\n\"R-right, Captain...\"\n\"Damn...we'll have to fight! They'll be tired from the march! Kill 'em!\"\n\"How considerate! We won't have to chase you down. Red Dragon Knights, draw arms!\"",
